---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="One Computer | Solusi IT Terpercaya">
    <main class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-neutral-950 text-neutral-300 selection:bg-green-500/30 pb-32">
        
        <div class="fixed inset-0 z-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:24px_24px]"></div>
        <div class="fixed inset-0 z-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_800px_at_50%_-30%,#064e3b,transparent)]"></div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl w-full z-10 space-y-12 pt-12 md:pt-24">
            
            <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-green-500 hover:text-green-400 transition-colors group font-mono">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
                </svg>
                KEMBALI KE BERANDA
            </a>

            <div class="space-y-4 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-8">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-green-500/30 bg-green-900/10 text-xs font-mono text-green-400">
                        IT SOLUTIONS & SERVICES
                    </span>
                    <span class="flex h-2 w-2 relative">
                        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
                        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500"></span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-xs text-green-500 font-mono tracking-widest uppercase">Toko Buka</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight">One Computer</h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
                    Toko kami bergerak di bidang penjualan dan servis komputer dengan komitmen menyediakan produk original, harga terjangkau, dan layanan terpercaya.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
                
                <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-12">
                    
                    <section class="space-y-6">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white font-tech flex items-center gap-2 uppercase tracking-wider">
                            <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span>
                            PRODUK & LAYANAN
                        </h2>
                        
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all">
                                <h3 class="text-green-400 font-bold mb-2">Penjualan Unit</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Laptop baru/second, PC Build-up, Rakitan Gaming, dan Office Desktop.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all">
                                <h3 class="text-green-400 font-bold mb-2">Hardware Service</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Perbaikan motherboard, ganti LCD, keyboard, upgrade SSD/RAM, dan pembersihan total.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all">
                                <h3 class="text-green-400 font-bold mb-2">Software Solution</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Instalasi OS, Office, Driver, hingga pembuatan website dan aplikasi kustom.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all">
                                <h3 class="text-green-400 font-bold mb-2">Aksesoris & Sparepart</h3>
                                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">Printer, Tinta, Mouse, Keyboard, Charger, dan berbagai suku cadang komputer.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="space-y-6">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white font-tech flex items-center gap-2 uppercase tracking-wider">
                            <span class="w-1 h-6 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span>
                            LOKASI TOKO
                        </h2>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <p class="text-neutral-400 flex items-start gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/20">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-green-500 shrink-0"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
                                <span>Sindangreret, RT/RW 005/001 (Samping SMK Swadaya Karangnunggal), Tasikmalaya, Jawa Barat.</span>
                            </p>
                            <div class="w-full h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/50 group">
                                <iframe 
                                    src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d3954.832968393529!2d108.1196328!3d-7.6329699!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x0!2zN8KwMzcnNTguNyJTIDEwOMKwMDcnMTAuNyJF!5e0!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1710000000000!5m2!1sid!2sid" 
                                    class="w-full h-full grayscale invert opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity contrast-125"
                                    style="border:0;" 
                                    allowfullscreen="" 
                                    loading="lazy"
                                    referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
                                </iframe>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                </div>

                <div class="space-y-8">
                    
                    <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/30 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-6 shadow-xl">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white font-tech uppercase tracking-wider">INFORMASI LAYANAN</h3>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 font-mono mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Metode Pembayaran</div>
                                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 rounded text-[10px] text-green-500 font-mono">CASH</span>
                                    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 rounded text-[10px] text-green-500 font-mono">TRANSFER</span>
                                    <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 rounded text-[10px] text-green-500 font-mono">QRIS</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="w-full h-[1px] bg-neutral-800"></div>

                            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
                                    <span class="text-neutral-400">Garansi Servis Terjamin</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
                                    <span class="text-neutral-400">Layanan Panggilan ke Rumah</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
                                    <span class="text-neutral-400">Paket Servis Rutin Kantor</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <span class="text-green-500 font-bold">✓</span>
                                    <span class="text-neutral-400">Konsultasi IT Gratis</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl border border-green-500/30 bg-gradient-to-b from-green-900/10 to-neutral-900/50 relative overflow-hidden group shadow-2xl">
                        <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-green-500/20 rounded-full blur-[50px] group-hover:bg-green-500/30 transition-all"></div>

                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400 font-tech mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider relative z-10">KONSULTASI SEKARANG</h3>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-3 relative z-10">
                            <a href="https://wa.me/6285860565852?text=Halo%20One%20Computer,%20saya%20ingin%20tanya%20tentang%20layanan%20servis..." target="_blank" class="block w-full py-4 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-500 text-white font-bold text-center rounded-xl transition-all shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(22,163,74,0.3)] hover:scale-[1.02]">
                                CHAT WHATSAPP
                            </a>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <p class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500 font-mono">Respon Cepat: 08.00 - 17.00 WIB</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .font-tech {
        font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    }
</style>